Please implement the function according to the description and setup above. Output the code in a markdown code block, i.e., between triple backticks (```) with the language specified as Python.
Please only output code and not your natural language commentary.', "Let's refactor this code to improve its structure and maintainability. Could we extract the permission checking and document updating logic into separate pure functions? This will help in making the code more modular and easier to test, while keeping the main alter_document function's signature unchanged.
Please only output code and not your natural language commentary.", 'Can you add logging support to track document changes and user actions? This should include logging the operator ID, document ID, and a timestamp of when the document was altered. Ensure that the logging is clear and can be easily understood for auditing purposes.
Please only output code and not your natural language commentary.']
